8, 137.319, 136.7524, 137.3715, 137.7527, 138.5553, 138.7521, 139.5881, 139.3554, 139.8398, 139.9425, 141.3734, 139.9485, 138.5325, 138.44, 139.7867, 138.8543, 138.912, 140.1903, 140.4909, 141.2336, 142.4251, 143.815, 144.4769, 146.9708, 145.6086, 143.6982, 142.2718, 143.1498, 144.0407, 145.2414, 145.4526, 143.4414, 144.0155, 145.7625, 148.411, 148.4768, 146.9185, 146.3499, 147.2419, 147.836, 150.7168, 152.2697, 152.213, 152.6587, 155.6822, 155.6918, 155.4906, 158.2143, 158.1064, 155.703, 153.7968, 153.2684, 153.5541, 151.974, 151.6774, 150.6765, 153.3577, 153.0031, 153.4649, 152.6935, 153.2185, 151.7837, 152.3092, 151.6813, 152.0704, 153.6075, 153.7237, 153.5112, 153.0256, 155.6462, 159.7163, 159.0639, 157.8804, 156.7931, 157.8994, 155.6177, 157.53, 156.9306, 155.2907, 156.417, 157.5629, 157.1626, 159.8034, 160.9834, 160.8482, 164.3111, 164.6859, 167.3527, 164.456, 165.0099, 164.5081, 162.4382, 159.585, 156.2169, 155.1573, 154.4878, 152.9816, 149.8748, 152.0287, 149.3211, 151.0649, 153.0915, 150.6223, 147.8092, 151.0962, 151.9579, 156.1927, 156.8715, 160.6956, 163.979, 162.3272, 163.2869, 164.8088, 165.8714, 162.7932, 164.273, 165.8255, 167.5987, 167.3018, 168.7801, 167.823, 164.7715, 165.8424, 165.8733, 165.3426, 165.2278, 166.8405, 166.5205, 167.6853, 165.7696, 167.3207, 165.5783, 167.9483, 166.7821, 164.0666, 164.6796, 164.5127, 165.1319, 164.4105, 156.9911, 158.1288, 161.3233, 153.4479, 150.5672, 152.2642, 151.4598, 151.3048, 151.355, 152.0487, 149.7893, 147.6509, 149.224, 150.7126, 152.0975, 149.3193, 149.4594, 152.0936, 152.6826, 153.1056, 154.3021, 157.5341, 155.4619, 159.021, 156.1208, 157.3556, 156.4491, 155.1297, 153.7953, 151.4484, 150.3407, 149.8531, 146.8473, 148.3372, 149.3284, 148.5338, 150.603, 151.1135, 150.6575, 150.1292, 148.605], "summary_html": "<h1>基于主动买入行为的选股因子 -- 商品期货复现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告基于逐笔成交数据中的主动买卖标志（BS flag），构建了四类刻画投资者主动买入行为的因子。核心思路是：主动买入占比越高或主动买入强度越稳定的品种，反映了更强的资金流入意愿，未来收益更好（动量效应）。</p>\n<p>在商品期货复现中，我们使用 Level2 分钟盘口数据中的 <code>bamt</code>（主动买入金额）和 <code>samt</code>（主动卖出金额），聚合到日频后计算截面因子。最终\"日间净主买强度\"因子（离散多空模式）表现最优，Sharpe 0.79，最大回撤 -38%。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>10.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2720</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.63</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.97</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.44 / 0.78</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.18</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.27</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.1</span></td><td>1.0</td><td>0.6</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.21</span></td><td>0.51</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.36</span></td><td>1.8</td><td>1.81</td><td>0.77</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2722</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>16.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>6.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>四类因子定义如下：</p>\n<p><strong>因子 1: 主买占比</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{BuyRatio}_t = \\frac{\\sum_{\\text{min}} \\text{bamt}_{\\text{min}}}{\\sum_{\\text{min}} \\text{bamt}_{\\text{min}} + \\sum_{\\text{min}} \\text{samt}_{\\text{min}}}</div>\n<p>取 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 日滚动均值作为因子值：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{BuyRatio}_{t,N} = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{i=0}^{N-1} \\text{BuyRatio}_{t-i}</div>\n<p><strong>因子 2: 日间净主买强度</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{NetBuy}_t = \\sum_{\\text{min}} \\text{bamt}_{\\text{min}} - \\sum_{\\text{min}} \\text{samt}_{\\text{min}}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{NetBuyIntensity}_{t,N} = \\frac{\\text{mean}_{N}(\\text{NetBuy})}{\\text{std}_{N}(\\text{NetBuy})}</div>\n<p><strong>因子 3: 日间主买强度</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{BuyIntensity}_{t,N} = \\frac{\\text{mean}_{N}(\\text{bamt}_{\\text{daily}})}{\\text{std}_{N}(\\text{bamt}_{\\text{daily}})}</div>\n<p><strong>因子 4: 日间主买占比强度</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{BuyRatioIntensity}_{t,N} = \\frac{\\text{mean}_{N}(\\text{BuyRatio})}{\\text{std}_{N}(\\text{BuyRatio})}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.78)</strong>: 实现全部四类因子（主买占比、日间主买强度、日间净主买强度、日间主买占比强度），使用 10/20 日窗口，连续多空信号，20 日换仓。buy_ratio_10 最优 Sharpe 0.78。诊断发现：(1) 日换手率 1.19 偏高导致费用侵蚀；(2) 信号在部分品种有效（ts_IC 正值品种 57%）；(3) 2022-2023 年度 Sharpe 为负。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.78, 无提升)</strong>: 扩展参数网格至 5/10/20 日窗口 x 5/10/20/40 日换仓 x 正/反方向，共 16 个变体。发现：(1) 短期窗口（5日）表现差；(2) 反向信号（buy_intensity 反转）在商品中不适用（Sharpe &lt; 0）；(3) 连续信号下换手率无明显改善。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.79, 关键转折)</strong>: 针对高换手问题，引入离散多空模式（rank_to_ls, top/bottom 20%），同时测试降低 vol_target 和提高 min_ic 阈值。nbi10_ls_h20_raw 取得 Sharpe 0.79：离散信号降低了换仓间的微小变动，最大回撤从 -73% 大幅改善至 -38%。虽未突破 0.8 门槛，但风险调整后的改善显著。Pipeline 因连续两轮提升不足自动终止。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: Level2 分钟数据聚合到日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（70 个商品期货），使用 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原报告针对 A 股，移植到商品期货时因子动量效应有所减弱\n<p>- Level2 数据从 2012 年起可用（部分品种更晚），影响样本长度 - 2022-2023 年度表现为负，信号在不同市场状态下稳定性不足 - 与因子库最相似因子（COMB）相关系数仅 0.31，因子独立性良好</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 39.9s</li>\n</ul>"}